What is the projected market size & growth rate of the Blood Culture Test Market?

Market Analysis and Size

Rising prevalence of sepsis and other blood related infections is a root cause for the rise in blood culture test market value. Growing approval rate of new products, such as instruments and consumables for Bloodstream Infections (BSI) diagnosis will further create lucrative and remunerative opportunities for the Blood culture test market.

